videoDetails.Title: I SPENT 24 Hr grinding the WORST tech tree (warthunder)
videoDetails.Description:
If you're looking to see the worst tech tree in the Warthunder game, look no further! In this video, I spend 24 hours playing the worst tech tree in the game, and I'm almost done with it!

This Warthunder video is a real challenge! I'm playing through the worst tech tree in the game, and it's a lot of fun. If you're a Warthunder player, I recommend trying this out sometime. It's an interesting challenge!
